original: Forsbring, Axel Bertil Esaias, kyrkoherde, Grebo, f. 22/4/04 i Eksjö av musikfanj. Alfred F. o. Amanda Fors-bring. G. 32 m. Gunhild Bode-Lind-quist. Barn: Curt f. 33. — Stud:ex. i Lund 25, teol. fil. ex. 27, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov samt prästv. f. Linköp. stift 31. V. kommin. i Hällestad 31, kommin. i Skedevi 32, kyrkoh. i Grebo o. Värna sed. 40.
translated: Forsbring, Axel Bertil Esaias, pastor, Grebo, born on April 22nd, 1904 in Eksjö to musician Alfred F. and Amanda Forsbring. Married in 1932 to Gunhild Bode-Lindquist with one child named Curt, born in 1933. He graduated from Lund University in 1925, obtained a degree in theology in 1927, and passed the practical theology examination for the priesthood in the Linköping diocese in 1931. He was a curate in Hällestad in 1931, a curate in Skedevi in 1932, and has been the pastor in Grebo and Värna since 1940.
